{
    "info": {
        "_postman_id": "b3e1d318-5e3f-4d6a-8b2c-4cc2f5b12c54",
        "name": "MDD API",
        "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
    },
    "event": [
        {
            "listen": "prerequest",
            "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                    "// Ajoute le header X-XSRF-TOKEN avec la valeur de la variable globale xsrf_token si elle existe",
                    "var xsrf = pm.globals.get('xsrf_token');",
                    "if(xsrf){ pm.request.headers.upsert({ key: 'X-XSRF-TOKEN', value: xsrf }); }"
                ]
            }
        }
    ],
    "description": "\n# MDD API Postman Collection\n\n## Authentification\n\n- L'API utilise un cookie JWT pour l'authentification.\n- Le token CSRF est géré automatiquement par le backend (aucune action manuelle requise dans Postman).\n- Après login ou register, le cookie JWT est défini et utilisé pour toutes les requêtes protégées.\n- Les endpoints sont centralisés dans le backend via ApiEndpoints.java.\n\n## Variables\n\n- {{baseUrl}} : URL de base de l'API\n- {{jwt}} : token JWT (pour tests manuels, mais le cookie est prioritaire)\n- {{userId}}, {{topicId}}, {{articleId}}, {{commentId}} : valeurs dynamiques pour les tests.\n\n## Endpoints\n\n- Tous les chemins d'API sont alignés avec ApiEndpoints.java.\n- Les valeurs de test sont centralisées dans TestConstants.java.\n\n## Utilisation\n\n- Utilisez Register ou Login pour initialiser l'authentification.\n- Les scripts Postman gèrent automatiquement la récupération des variables nécessaires.\n- Pour tester les endpoints protégés, assurez-vous d'être authentifié (cookie JWT présent).\n\n",
    "variable": [
        {
            "key": "baseUrl",
            "value": "http://localhost:8080"
        },
        {
            "key": "jwt",
            "value": ""
        },
        {
            "key": "userId",
            "value": ""
        },
        {
            "key": "topicId",
            "value": ""
        },
        {
            "key": "articleId",
            "value": ""
        },
        {
            "key": "commentId",
            "value": ""
        },
        {
            "key": "username",
            "value": "kevin"
        },
        {
            "key": "email",
            "value": "kevin.renault@example.com"
        },
        {
            "key": "password",
            "value": "Password1!"
        }
    ],
    "auth": {
        "type": "bearer",
        "bearer": [
            {
                "key": "token",
                "value": "{{jwt}}",
                "type": "string"
            }
        ]
    },
    "item": [
        {
            "name": "Auth",
            "item": [
                {
                    "name": "Get CSRF Token (public) - sets XSRF-TOKEN",
                    "event": [
                        {
                            "listen": "test",
                            "script": {
                                "type": "text/javascript",
                                "exec": [
                                    "pm.test('Status 200', function () { pm.response.to.have.status(200); });",
                                    "var xsrfCookie = pm.cookies.get('XSRF-TOKEN');",
                                    "pm.test('Has XSRF-TOKEN cookie', function () { pm.expect(xsrfCookie).to.exist; });",
                                    "if(xsrfCookie){ pm.globals.set('xsrf_token', xsrfCookie); }"
                                ]
                            }
                        }
                    ],
                    "request": {
                        "method": "GET",
                        "url": {
                            "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/csrf",
                            "host": [
                                "{{baseUrl}}"
                            ],
                            "path": [
                                "api",
                                "auth",
                                "csrf"
                            ]
                        }
                    }
                },
                {
                    "name": "Register (public) - sets {{jwt}} + {{userId}}",
                    "event": [
                        {
                            "listen": "test",
                            "script": {
                                "type": "text/javascript",
                                "exec": [
                                    "pm.test('Status 200', function () { pm.response.to.have.status(200); });",
                                    "var json = pm.response.json();",
                                    "pm.test('Has token', function () { pm.expect(json).to.have.property('token'); });",
                                    "if (json && json.token) { pm.collectionVariables.set('jwt', json.token); }",
                                    "if (json && json.user && json.user.id) { pm.collectionVariables.set('userId', json.user.id); }"
                                ]
                            }
                        }
                    ],
                    "request": {
                        "auth": {
                            "type": "noauth"
                        },
                        "method": "POST",
                        "header": [
                            {
                                "key": "Content-Type",
                                "value": "application/json"
                            }
                        ],
                        "body": {
                            "mode": "raw",
                            "raw": "{\n  \"username\": \"{{username}}\",\n  \"email\": \"{{email}}\",\n  \"password\": \"{{password}}\"\n}"
                        },
                        "url": {
                            "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register",
                            "host": [
                                "{{baseUrl}}"
                            ],
                            "path": [
                                "api",
                                "auth",
                                "register"
                            ]
                        }
                    }
                },
                {
                    "name": "Login (public) - sets {{jwt}} + {{userId}}",
                    "event": [
                        {
                            "listen": "test",
                            "script": {
                                "type": "text/javascript",
                                "exec": [
                                    "pm.test('Status 200', function () { pm.response.to.have.status(200); });",
                                    "var json = pm.response.json();",
                                    "pm.test('Has token', function () { pm.expect(json).to.have.property('token'); });",
                                    "if (json && json.token) { pm.collectionVariables.set('jwt', json.token); }",
                                    "if (json && json.user && json.user.id) { pm.collectionVariables.set('userId', json.user.id); }"
                                ]
                            }
                        }
                    ],
                    "request": {
                        "auth": {
                            "type": "noauth"
                        },
                        "method": "POST",
                        "header": [
                            {
                                "key": "Content-Type",
                                "value": "application/json"
                            }
                        ],
                        "body": {
                            "mode": "raw",
                            "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"{{email}}\",\n  \"password\": \"{{password}}\"\n}"
                        },
                        "url": {
                            "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login",
                            "host": [
                                "{{baseUrl}}"
                            ],
                            "path": [
                                "api",
                                "auth",
                                "login"
                            ]
                        }
                    }
                },
                {
                    "name": "Me (protected)",
                    "request": {
                        "method": "GET",
                        "url": {
                            "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/me",
                            "host": [
                                "{{baseUrl}}"
                            ],
                            "path": [
                                "api",
                                "auth",
                                "me"
                            ]
                        }
                    }
                },
                {
                    "name": "Logout (protected) - clears {{jwt}}",
                    "event": [
                        {
                            "listen": "test",
                            "script": {
                                "type": "text/javascript",
                                "exec": [
                                    "pm.test('Status 204', function () { pm.response.to.have.status(204); });",
                                    "pm.collectionVariables.unset('jwt');"
                                ]
                            }
                        }
                    ],
                    "request": {
                        "method": "POST",
                        "url": {
                            "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/logout",
                            "host": [
